# Sales Data Analysis & Dashboard Project

## Overview
This project performs end-to-end sales data analysis using structured datasets.
It includes data cleaning, exploratory analysis, metric computation, and
interactive dashboard creation to generate business insights.

The objective of this project is to analyze sales performance across
customers, products, regions, and salespersons and present insights
through visual dashboards.

---

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- SQLAlchemy
- MySQL
- Power BI
- Jupyter Notebook
- VS Code

