## Data Analysis Performed
- Data loading and preprocessing using Pandas
- Handling missing values and validation checks
- Joining multiple datasets using relational keys
- Sales analysis by:
  - Region
  - Product
  - Salesperson
  - Customer
- Revenue and performance metric calculations
- Exploratory data analysis and visualizations

---

## Dashboarding
An interactive Power BI dashboard was created to visualize key business metrics.

### Dashboard Highlights
- Total Revenue and Sales KPIs
- Region-wise sales comparison
- Product performance analysis
- Salesperson performance tracking
- Interactive filters for dynamic analysis

The dashboard enables stakeholders to monitor performance and identify trends effectively.

